otball team|Germany]] in 2011]]\n{{updated|16 November 2019}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Manuel Neuer|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=26616|website=EU-Football.info|accessdate=4 November 2015}}</ref>\n[[File:Award ceremony of the World Cup in Brazil 04.jpg|thumb|Neuer celebrating after [[Germany national football team|Germany's]] 1\u20130 victory over [[Argentina national football team|Argentina]] in the [[2014 FIFA World Cup Final|FIFA World Cup Final]].]]\n{| class=\"wikitable\" Style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | [[Germany national football team|Germany]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2009||2||0\n|-\n|2010||13||0\n|-\n|2011||10||0\n|-\n|2012||11||0\n|-\n|2013||8||0\n|-\n|2014||13||0\n|-\n|2015||6||0\n|-\n|2016||11||0\n|-\n|2017||0||0\n|-\n|2018||10||0\n|-\n|2019||8||0\n|-\n!Total||92||0\n|}\n\n== Honours ==\n'''Schalke 04'''<ref name=\"fussballdaten.de\">{{cite web | url = http://www.fussballdaten.de/spieler/neuermanuel/2013/ | title = Manuel Neuer | language = de | publisher = fussballdaten.de | accessdate = 14 July 2014}}</ref>\n* [[DFB-Pokal]]: [[2010\u201311 DFB-Pokal|2010\u201311]]\n* [[DFB-Ligapokal]]: [[2005 DFB-Ligapokal|2005]]\n\n'''Bayern Munich'''<ref name=\"fussballdaten.de\"/>\n* [[Bundesliga]]: [[2012\u201313 Bundesliga|2012\u201313]], [[2013\u201314 Bundesliga|2013\u201314]], [[2014\u201315 Bundesliga|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Bundesliga|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 Bundesliga|2016\u201317]], [[2017\u201318 Bundesliga|2017\u201318]], [[2018\u201319 Bundesliga|2018\u201319]]\n* [[DFB-Pokal]]: [[2012\u201313 DFB-Pokal|2012\u201313]], [[2013\u201314 DFB-Pokal|2013\u201314]], [[2015\u201316 DFB-Pokal|2015\u201316]], [[2018\u201319 DFB-Pokal|2018\u201319]]\n* [[DFL-Supercup]]: [[2012 DFL-Supercup|2012]], [[2016 DFL-Supercup|2016]], [[2017 DFL-Supercup|2017]], [[2018 DFL-Supercup|2018]]\n* [[UEFA Champions League]]: [[2012\u201313 UEFA Champions League|2012\u201313]]\n* [[UEFA Super Cup]]: [[2013 UEFA Super Cup|2013]]\n* [[FIFA Club World Cup]]: [[2013 FIFA Club World Cup|2013]]\n\n'''Germany'''<ref name=\"fussballdaten.de\" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.welt.de/sport/article116793792/Khedira-Oezil-Neuer-Aufstieg-der-Euro-Helden.html | title = Khedira, \u00d6zil, Neuer \u2013 Aufstieg der Euro-Helden | language = de | work = Die Welt | date = 6 June 2013 | accessdate = 17 July 2014 | first = Lars | last = Gartenschl\u00e4ger}}</ref>\n* [[FIFA World Cup]]: [[2014 FIFA World Cup|2014]]\n* [[UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship]]: [[2009 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2009]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n* [[Silbernes Lorbeerblatt]]: 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rp-online.de/sport/fussball/nationalelf/wm/dfb/DFB-Elf-erhaelt-Silbernes-Lorbeerblatt_bid_59101.html|title=DFB-Elf erh\u00e4lt Silbernes Lorbeerblatt|accessdate=19 December 2010|language=German|work=[[Rheinische Post]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229043204/http://www.rp-online.de/sport/fussball/nationalelf/wm/dfb/DFB-Elf-erhaelt-Silbernes-Lorbeerblatt_bid_59101.html|archive-date=29 December 2010|url-status=dead}}</ref> 2014<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.welt.de/sport/fussball/wm-2014/article134192440/Heute-sagt-Ihr-Land-Ihnen-Dankeschoen.html|title=\"Heute sagt Ihr Land Ihnen Dankesch\u00f6n\"| date = 10 November 2014 | access-date=7 September 2016 | first = Lars | last = Wallrodt | language = German | website = [[Die Welt]]}}</ref>\n* [[Footballer of the Year in Germany]]: 2011,<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/555828/artikel_manuel-neuer-ist-fussballspieler-des-jahres.html | title = Manuel Neuer ist \"Fu\u00dfballer des Jahres\" | language = de | publisher = kicker.de | date = 31 July 2014 | accessdate = 18 July 2014}}</ref> 2014<ref name=\"Manuel Neuer named German Footballer of the Year\"/>\n* [[European Sports Media#ESM Team of the Year|ESM Team of the Year]]: [[European Sports Magazines#2011\u201312|2011\u201312]],<ref name=el>{{cite web |