aly]]\n[[Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Ukrainian football managers]]\n[[Category:Ukraine national football team managers]]\n[[Category:Ukraine \u2013 Forward! politicians]]\n[[Category:Ukrainian sportsperson-politicians]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the title of Hero of Ukraine]]\n", "name_user": "S.A. Julio", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eInternational career:fixing URL scheme, other genfixes", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andriy_Shevchenko"}
